*&quot;Almaden is My Life&quot; (1984), by Ruth Teiser, Morris H. Katz, William A. Dieppe
*&quot;New Almaden&quot; (2006) by Michael Boulland
*&quot;Memoir On the Mines and Works of Almaden&quot; (2010), by H Kuss

