==Release==
&quot;Just One of the Guys&quot; was released on April 26, 1985. Although the film was not successful in theaters, it was in heavy rotation on HBO and Cinemax for several years thereafter (airing after Sherilynn Fenn had gained stardom on &quot;Twin Peaks&quot; in 1990).

===Home media===
The film was released on Blu-ray Disc under Sony Pictures on April 28, 2020. Special features include filmmaker and cast commentary and theatrical trailer.

==Reception==
On the review aggregator website Rotten Tomatoes, the film holds an approval rating of 57% based on 14 reviews, with an average rating of 4.8/10. Metacritic, which uses a weighted average, assigned the film a score of 57 based on 6 critics, indicating &quot;mixed or average&quot; reviews.

