formula_103
so the new generalized coordinates and momenta are &quot;constants&quot; of motion. As they are constants, in this context the new generalized momenta formula_104 are usually denoted formula_82, i.e. formula_106 and the new generalized coordinates formula_107 are typically denoted as formula_108, so formula_109.

